d @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--frag, relating to a woman with the cognomen Prima. The only other surviving element is the name Paternus (Paternu[s]) on line 2. Given the palaeographic date, can't be linked to Iulius Paternus of the later inscr.; but still quality of the fr. implies the 'medioalti' of Catania.-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7085\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>32\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":[